title: Lamar Odom Found Unconscious in Nevada Brothel
text: Lamar Odom Found Unconscious in Nevada Brothel Lamar Odom has been found unconscious and unable to breathe at a Nevada brothel, TMZ r... Comment Posted Oct. 14, 2015 at 12:01 AM Updated at 1:36 AM Posted Oct. 14, 2015 at 12:01 AM Updated at 1:36 AM Â» Social News Lamar Odom has been found unconscious and unable to breathe at a Nevada brothel, TMZ reports. Odom arrived at Dennis Hof's Love Ranch South on Saturday, taking an herbal substitute for Viagra. On Tuesday afternoon, a woman entered Odom's VIP suite and found him unconscious. When the manager of the facility arrived, he discovered a "mucus-type liquid coming out of his nose and mouth." Odom was taken by ambulance to a Pahrump, Nev., hospital where he was intubated and was then airlifted to a Las Vegas hospital for more treatment. Sources say that his condition is "not good."
